chidb - A didactic RDBMS
=====================================

The chidb documentation is available at http://chi.cs.uchicago.edu/

## Quick Start

### Preparation

```
./autogen.sh
./configure
make
```

### Run

```
./chidb
```

### Check

```
make check
```

